reviews.text: fantastic restaurant. they fitted me in even though the online booking service said they were full.  service was great and the food was lush. it's a good job joe public can't find it unless they know where they're going.  secreted in a building between bars, with no signs, just a 'secret' lift to the fourth floor. it was definitely a hidden gem.
Excellent lunch buffet. Top notch selection. They brought extra items to our table, which was a nice touch. Good environment compared with other Indian restaurants in central.
Lovely indian cuisine. Great atmosphere. Amazing food highly recommended. Super enjoyable night!
Food is acceptable. The entire place especially bathrooms need a deep clean. Amiable staff.

Nice Indian buffet restaurant. Good variety of food for both vegetarians and non-vegetarians. Would definitely recommend to try. I think they started cooking less spicy food so that everybody who is not used to the spicy food can eat. Drinks are also available. Bit difficult to find. Enjoyed my time there and definitely planning to visit again.
